A conversation with @michaelhewettmusic @vesselacademy on What is a Master Yoga Class? 
A master is someone who is intimately bound up with beginner's mind. And to discover what is the most exciting in the present moment. They know how to open to curiosity. Turn off their narrative and be the hollow bone that the Universe uses as Her finely tuned instrument.
 
  This class is all about discovering curiosity. to have the fresh ideas and excitement that a child would have when they get excited. Yoga means to connect. It brings us to in touch with that aliveness, so if you are a beginner going to a master class, know that you will be experiencing a longer class (90mins) so we can go deeper. 

💎 Registration with link in header 

Hope you can join us on this amazing opportunity to explore your inner self 🧿

Date: Friday Dec 10th 7pm - 8:30pm 
Address: Form + Flow 2705 41st Ave. LIC. NY

Step into a moment of stillness and beauty. @marta_cascales_alimbau offers an immersive and meditative piano experience where you’re invited to lie down, close your eyes, and simply receive.

This isn’t a concert — it’s a space to pause, feel, and reconnect with subtle emotions often lost in the noise of everyday life.
 
Marta is a Barcelona-born, New York-based pianist and composer whose delicate blend of classical, contemporary, and minimalist music has touched millions. With over 5 million streams on Spotify and a debut on the iconic label Deutsche Grammophon, her sound resonates deeply and gently — a balm for the soul.

Friday, July 11 & 25 @ 7:30 - 8:30pm

Join us for an evening of heart-centered community, rooted in the sacred practice of kirtan, a devotional call-and-response chanting tradition from Bhakti yoga. @authorlukema 
 
Through shared mantra, rhythm, and voice, kirtan helps quiet the mind, uplift the spirit, and open the heart — no singing experience needed, just your presence and openness.
 
To begin the evening, we’ll share a ceremonial cacao offering — a sacred plant medicine revered by Indigenous Mesoamerican cultures. 

While not traditionally part of kirtan, we offer cacao with deep respect, as a gentle support to awaken the voice, deepen presence, and soften into heartfelt connection.
 
Come as you are. Leave more connected — to yourself, to each other, and to the sacred through sound.

#kirtan #bhakti #yoga #mantra #music #sound #cacao

Join us this Sunday for a Rooftop Pilates class led by Jessanya @jessanyaxx at @noble_lic . We’re keeping a close eye on the weather—if it rains 🌧, the class will move indoors to our Queensbridge studio.
 
@jessanyaxx Jessanya is a 500-hour RYT and certified mat Pilates instructor with extensive mentorship and continued studies that support her multidimensional approach to teaching. Her classes are a fusion of strength, softness, and intuitive flow — designed to move energy, awaken presence and guide students toward their own inner essence.
 
Whether she’s leading a dynamic vinyasa sequence or a slow, grounded practice, Jessanya creates space for transformation through breath, mindfulness, and embodied movement.
 
Beyond the studio, you’ll often find her walking barefoot in nature, dancing freely, or laughing with her whole body alongside the people she loves.

#yoga #rooftopyoga #pilates #yogastudio #longislandcity
